<h2>Authorize apps</h2>
<p>
    In order to connect your app to lager, you have to configure it here. Lager will then give you an auth token, which you will append to your http requests to lager, like so 
    <code>?auth=AUTH_CODE</code>.
</p>
<p>
    <ul>
        <li><a href="/auth/register">Register your app</a></li>
        <li><a href="/auth/list">View currently registered apps</a></li>
        <li><a href="/auth/revoke">Revoke access to an app</a></li>
    </ul>
</p>